    <div class="container">
        <h1>Template 2: The Project Kick-Off</h1>
        <p class="intro">
            Based on Chapter 7, send this message *immediately* after accepting the offer. 
            It prevents "scope creep" and positions you as a proactive partner, not just "hired help."
        </p>

        <div class="template-box">
            <h2>Subject: Project Kick-Off: <span class="placeholder">[Project Name]</span> Confirmation & Next Steps</h2>
            
            <p>Hi <span class="placeholder">[Client Name]</span>,</p>

            <p>
                Thank you again for choosing me for the <span class="placeholder">[Project Name]</span> project! 
                I'm genuinely excited to collaborate with you.
            </p>
            <p>
                Just to confirm our understanding and ensure we are perfectly aligned, here is my summary of the project:
            </p>

            <ul>
                <li><strong>Scope:</strong> <span class="placeholder">[Reiterate the exact scope, e.g., 'Translation of the 10-page Informed Consent Form from Hebrew to English.']</span></li>
                <li><strong>Deliverable(s):</strong> <span class="placeholder">[List specific file formats, e.g., 'One .docx file with the final translation and one .docx file with tracked changes.']</span></li>
                <li><strong>Timeline:</strong> <span class="placeholder">[Confirm the final deadline, e.g., 'Final delivery by EOD Tuesday, November 5th.']</span></li>
                <li><strong>Fee:</strong> <span class="placeholder">[Confirm the agreed price, e.g., '$XXX Fixed Price' or '$XX/hour for the first milestone.']</span></li>
            </ul>

            <p>
                To ensure I tailor the output perfectly to your needs, I just have two quick clarifying questions:
            </p>
            
            <ol style="padding-left: 25px;">
                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong><span class="placeholder">[Your first smart, insightful question, e.g., 'Is there a specific style guide or glossary I should follow?']</span></strong></li>
                <li><strong><span class="placeholder">[Your second relevant question, e.g., 'Could you briefly describe the primary target audience for the final document?']</span></strong></li>
            </ol>

            <p>
                My process will involve <span class="placeholder">[Briefly mention your process, e.g., 'initial translation, followed by terminology research, and a final two-stage proofreading pass to ensure 100% accuracy']</span>. 
                I will provide a mid-point update if the project extends beyond a few days.
            </p>
            <p>
                I'll be primarily available via <span class="placeholder">[Platform Name, e.g., 'Upwork messages']</span> during my working hours 
                <span class="placeholder">[Your Timezone, e.g., '(ART, GMT-3)']</span>. Please don't hesitate to reach out with any questions.
            </p>

            <p>
                Looking forward to a successful collaboration!
            </p>
            
            <p>
                Best regards,<br>
                Danilo Hurwitz
            </p>
